{"tid":1573513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新地星期四開售匯璽三期，我哋要唔要去睇樓？","createTime":"2019-09-16T04:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:49:21.000Z","uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f94353341a5adf7b86f59e1e2062da7a89d99f1","tid":1573513,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"作為熱愛祖國的連登巴打，星期四開始去入飛支持下愛國愛港的新地係好正常的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新地(00016)旗下長沙灣南昌站上蓋項目匯璽 III 加推176伙,發展商提供最高20%折扣,另提供匯璽 Fans 折扣及額外現金折扣,以基本折扣20%計算,折實平均呎價2.434萬元,較首批折實平均呎價2.1722萬元,高出約12%。<br />\n<br />\n最平入場費為8座8樓 D 室,實用面積275方呎,定價768.6萬元，折實售價614.88萬元，呎價22359元。<br />\n<br />\n新地代理副總經理唐錦江表示,項目截至今午4時,累計收約2500票,當中47%來自九龍區,38%來自新界區。"},{"pid":"ee0649a9df79fab3aa7323bbba201c2b5c21c586","tid":1573513,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/so4yF19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fso4yF19.jpg&h=481fa700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n921民間活動<br />\n下午1:00機場交通壓力測試<br />\n晚上7:00毋忘721元朗恐襲<br />\n928民間活動<br />\n下午1:00機場交通壓力測試<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkpicnic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpicnic&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=5f652094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpicnic</a><br />\n【訂閱野餐頻道】 @hkpicnic<br />\n✅ 接收各種活動資訊<br />\n✅ 如何安全地發夢<br />\n✅ 逃生、自衛等有用貼士"},{"pid":"b89d73fd2331c1e7b5a53a5f605e9f6d165734e8","tid":1573513,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"記得去售樓處排隊睇樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5cd6c5fb567fe635e19c4e7274c8035a2a965b","tid":1573513,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /